  "description": "Trefoil at low-moderate tangle (0.4) with maximum warmth — high dampening (0.7), 28ms delay base, filter at 4kHz, diffusion at 0.65. The crossing points are softened to velvet. Long 6-second release lets the resonances trail into silence gracefully. For producers who need textural pads that don't cut through.",
